{"tid":2056482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴一年】黃子悅受手足啟發欲戰立會：被捕素人付出更值關注","createTime":"2020-06-08T17:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T20:56:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94ab80face58f3ab0ab98109c385d396410da3f7","tid":2056482,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200609/XJQ5DPNFCCM54PNHESS7XGI6HM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FXJQ5DPNFCCM54PNHESS7XGI6HM%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19itC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=1da2fd57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FXJQ5DPNFCCM54PNHESS7XGI6HM%2F&h=1fbef435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200609/XJQ5DPNFCCM54PNHESS7XGI6HM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c9k7I1KUQ8OM_U_Lq_XWK2sAx2I=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3XIA5YKP4SDLHRUGOY6DR3CTI4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc9k7I1KUQ8OM_U_Lq_XWK2sAx2I%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3XIA5YKP4SDLHRUGOY6DR3CTI4.png&h=b8b35ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年6月政府強推《逃犯條例》激起連場抗爭，一年間被捕人數超過8,000人，被控暴動的更接近600人，被捕者中不乏熟悉的社運面孔，其中前學民思潮發言人黃子悅在理大圍攻當日被捕，被控暴動罪。黃子悅接受《蘋果》訪問指，雖然過去半年被官司糾纏，但同時令她認識到同受政治檢控的「手足」，與「手足」相處過程啟發她為被捕者發聲，包括考慮參與立法會選舉，強調被捕素人的付出值得更多人關注。"},{"pid":"52bd2fea227f793a94e4af6c5103afa26cc1e283","tid":2056482,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"每人一小步都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好睇小陳同佳粒墨效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5b5087350f153fb2a412a54582c64c9f4f776d","tid":2056482,"uid":131282,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"